      "parameters": {
        "content": "# Lesson 19 - Knowledge Base Chatbot - Qdrant\n## AI Automation\nSamantha Smith\n12/15/2025\n\nA Chatbot for GreenBite Kitchen --- a fictitious vegan fast-food restaurant.\n\n* User communicates with bot via Slack (see [ssmith-workflow-output](https://app.slack.com/client/T09QNL5T4GY/C09T3BH7KFC) private Slack channel.\n* Context based on the restaurant's Knowledge Base, FAQs, and Pricing Menu.\n* Thisi workflow can handle uploading multiple PDF documents at once.\n\nThe workflow includes an AI RAG Agent utilizing \n* Chat GPT 4.1-mini (OpenRouter)\n* Redis Chat memory\n* Qdrant Vector store\n\nCreating the Supbase Vector store involves:\n* Querying Google Drive folder for available files\n* Checking if that file is listed in a DB table as no having been uploaded\n* If file not yet uploaded, add it to DB table\n* Process each individual file by downloading it from Google Drive,\nextracting data and uploading it to Supabase as embeddings",
        "height": 640,
        "width": 896
      },
